# Ignore large installers and binaries
*.exe
*.msi
*.mp4
*.zip
*.rar
*.tar.gz

# Ignore exceptionally large PDFs (we'll ignore the ones > 100MB manually if needed, but standard is fine unless it fails)
Business Partner C1 Coursebook (unknown) (Z-Library).pdf

